<span class='line-number'>10</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>tutorial/
</span><span class='line'>  scrapy.cfg            # deploy configuration file
</span><span class='line'>  tutorial/             # project&rsquo;s Python module, you&rsquo;ll import your code from here
</span><span class='line'>      <strong>init</strong>.py
</span><span class='line'>      items.py          # project items file
</span><span class='line'>      pipelines.py      # project pipelines file
</span><span class='line'>      settings.py       # project settings file
</span><span class='line'>      spiders/          # a directory where you&rsquo;ll later put your spiders
</span><span class='line'>          <strong>init</strong>.py
</span><span class='line'>          &hellip;</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>定义抓取目标（Item）

<ul>
<li>本实例暂不使用</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>定义自己的爬虫(Spiders)

<ol>
<li>在spiders文件夹下新建spider.py文件</li>
<li>定义一个继承scrapy.Spider的BlogSpider类</li>
<li>定义BlogSpider类的name(名称)，start_urls(抓取网页url)和parse方法(对抓到的页面html的处理)
<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
